Shopping
Boutiques, Galleries, & More
end:views/snippets/arts/hero
Explore Martin County’s Unique Shops
Much like Martin County itself, shopping on the Treasure Coast
has something for everyone. Delightful shops, charming antique stores, art galleries, quaint cafes, and restaurants share the streets with name brand stores. From the trendy racks of the Treasure Coast Square Mall and the upscale boutiques of Harbour Bay Plaza to the eclectic shops in downtown Stuart and Jensen Beach, you’ll find a mix of charm and sophistication around every corner. Walkable, tree-lined streets, public art, and authentic Florida architecture only adds to the unique ambiance.
View All Shops
Must-Visit Shopping Spots
Explore the best of local style and small-town charm in our top shopping destinations.
Explore Stuart
Downtown Stuart
Explore Hobe Sound
Downtown Hobe Sound
Explore Jensen Beach
Downtown Jensen Beach
Explore Sewall's Point
Harbour Bay Plaza
Market on Main
Every Sunday morning, Downtown Stuart comes alive with
Market on Main
, a lively open-air market along the scenic waterfront. From 9am-1pm in Flagler Park, shop fresh produce, handmade goods, local art, and unique gifts all while enjoying the welcoming charm of this coastal community.
Explore More
Looking for More Local Finds?
From hidden gem boutiques to seasonal market roundups, our blog is full of inspiration for shopping around Martin County. Explore stories, gift guides, and insider tips to help you shop like a local.
Explore More
Your Shopping Adventure Awaits
Whether you’re searching for the perfect souvenir, a locally made gift, or a little something just for you—Martin County’s shops are full of unexpected delights.
View Shops

Contact Us
The Martin County Office of Tourism and Marketing is the official tourism marketing arm of Martin County, Florida. The goal of the Office of Tourism and Marketing is to provide information to those interested in visiting Martin County. We love to spread the word about this one of a kind destination.  Please contact us at info (at) discovermartin (dot) com or at 1-877-585-0085 / 772-288-5445 if you need any additional information or have any comments, suggestions or ideas. You can also follow us socially @discovermartin. Contact us to plan your
best Florida vacation yet.
